title: Warwick is the number 1 jungler in soloQ with a 55% winrate and rising

embed.description: League of Legends Statistics including Win Rate, Ban Rate, Play Rate, Kills, Deaths by Champions and the roles they play.

body:
Has moved 12 spots to be number 1 with a 55% win rate and rising.

TBH i'm a little scared of Warwick, if you let the game go beyond 30min he is almost unkillable

ALSO

Kayle has moved 26 spots to be the number 3 with a 53% win rate and rising

Xin Zhao has moved 17 spots to number 6 with a 53% win rate and rising.

replies.body: Ok this is getting really ridiculous sated devourer is OP and needs to be nerfed
get your freelo now, warwick is op in bronze and silver

plat and up.

EDIT:
bronze to diamond.. after that well...

All Devourer Junglers go up. Tank jungler are out pretty much.

Can't remember the last time I saw Sejuani pick or banned.

Shyvanna the new permaban.

http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/96809934/200474676

Tank junglers are still here :P

But yeah devourer junglers are a pain.

her damage is huge if she goes full damage

i seen her one shot the big krugg

yeah everyone agrees this new sated devourer isnt the way to go to just fix the jungle, or get rid of the tank meta for now, but thats what the meta is, you play to its strengths and you play to riots rules. if warwicks strong right now play him or prepare to play against him
(hint: play him, ive solo'd baron at 22 minutes, might be able to get 20 when fed, with sated, bork and another LS item or a visage)
I hate it when warwick becomes viable, let alone OP
